reviews.review_text: This is the one you want I don't know how Keith pulls better tape from the section than other people pull from FOB, but he does.
thank you !!!!! Keith I just got my second ipod (this one being 120GB), and all I can say is thank you!!!!  Your recordings are clearly superioir.

Superlative The recording needs a fair amount of EQing, and the ear needs some time to acclimatize, but after that it's a tremendous show, even with really nothing pulled out in the way of unusual songs.
